Larry Gerald MAYNES v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 7255. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. April 19, 1963. Donald S. Molen, Denver, Colo., for appellant. Lawrence M. Henry, U. S. Atty., and Michael C. Villano, Asst. U. S. Atty., Denver, Colo., for appellee.

Before PICKETT and SETH, Circuit Judges, and CHRISTENSEN, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed April 19, 1963, on motion of appellant,
